<span id="freeTextContainer12884034059367527749">LANGOLIERS and SECRET WINDOW, SECRET GARDEN were 4 star reads for me. They were really creepy and thrilling novellas that I quite enjoyed.<br/><br/>I would give 2 stars to THE LIBRARY POLICEMAN and THE SUN DOG, because I found them very tedious to get through although I overall liked the cast in both novellas. However, both stories took a path that is not my cup of tea.</span>

